    <item>
      <title>New look for OAuth tokens management</title>
      <link>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/06-05-oauth-tokens-new-interface/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Jun 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>//localhost:1313/changelog/2025/06-05-oauth-tokens-new-interface/</guid>
      <description>
        
        
        &lt;p&gt;After &lt;a href=&#34;//localhost:1313/developers/changelog/2025/05-28-oauth-consumer-new-interface/&#34; &gt;renewing OAuth consumers management&lt;/a&gt;, we&amp;rsquo;ve just updated the &lt;a href=&#34;https://console.clever-cloud.com/users/me/oauth-tokens&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;OAuth tokens section&lt;/a&gt; of users profile. It&amp;rsquo;s where you can see applications linked to your Clever Cloud account: Clever Tools, the Console or those linked to other OAuth consumers. You can still see creation and expiration date, last usage, revoke any or all of them… but in a clearer interface.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We also added a link to Clever Cloud&amp;rsquo;s OAuth tokens documentation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://www.clever-cloud.com/developers/api/howto/#oauth1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Learn more about OAuth tokens&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;//localhost:1313/images/changelog/console-new-oauth-tokens.webp&#34; alt=&#34;New OAuth tokens interface&#34; loading=&#34;lazy&#34; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

      </description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
